# Sample API Tests

This demonstrates using the `.rest` extension as an alternative to `.resty`.

## Quick Tests

```yaml
test: simple-get
get: https://httpbin.org/status/200
```

```yaml
test: echo-test
post: https://httpbin.org/anything
body: |
  {
    "message": "Testing .rest extension",
    "timestamp": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z"
  }
capture:
  # Extract the HTTP method from the response using JSONPath
  request_method: $.method
```
